{"data":{"repository":{"pullRequest":{"reviewThreads":{"nodes":[{"id":"PRRT_kwDOCG4DHc6FWlEK","isResolved":true,"comments":{"nodes":[{"databaseId":3316757576,"author":{"login":"cursor"},"body":"### Slide tracking ref never resets across market navigations\n\n**Medium Severity**\n\n<!-- DESCRIPTION START -->\nThe `hasTrackedSlide` ref is never reset when `currentMarket` changes. Since `navigation.navigate` reuses the existing `MARKET_DETAILS` screen instance (no `push`, no `getId` on the route), and no `key` prop is provided on `PerpsRelatedMarkets`, the component stays mounted across market-to-market navigations. After the first scroll on any market's rail, `hasTrackedSlide.current` remains `true` permanently, silently suppressing slide analytics for all subsequent market detail pages in the session.\n<!-- DESCRIPTION END -->\n\n<!-- BUGBOT_BUG_ID: 8ea04429-0b65-451c-8b5e-9afb2262f720 -->\n\n<!-- LOCATIONS START\napp/components/UI/Perps/components/PerpsRelatedMarkets/PerpsRelatedMarkets.tsx#L65-L66\napp/components/UI/Perps/Views/PerpsMarketDetailsView/PerpsMarketDetailsView.tsx#L1475-L1480\nLOCATIONS END -->\n<details>\n<summary>Additional Locations (1)</summary>\n\n- [`app/components/UI/Perps/Views/PerpsMarketDetailsView/PerpsMarketDetailsView.tsx#L1475-L1480`](https://github.com/MetaMask/metamask-mobile/blob/7652c52637f45f3f7be9193ea1b16b9cac7c25b5/app/components/UI/Perps/Views/PerpsMarketDetailsView/PerpsMarketDetailsView.tsx#L1475-L1480)\n\n</details>\n\n<div><a href=\"https://cursor.com/open?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-light.png\"><img alt=\"Fix in Cursor\" width=\"115\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-cursor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-light.png\"><img alt=\"Fix in Web\" width=\"99\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-dark.png\"></picture></a></div>\n\n\n<sup>Reviewed by [Cursor Bugbot](https://cursor.com/bugbot) for commit 7652c52637f45f3f7be9193ea1b16b9cac7c25b5. Configure [here](https://www.cursor.com/dashboard/bugbot).</sup>\n","path":"app/components/UI/Perps/components/PerpsRelatedMarkets/PerpsRelatedMarkets.tsx","line":58,"outdated":false,"createdAt":"2026-05-28T09:32:34Z"},{"databaseId":3317017070,"author":{"login":"abretonc7s"},"body":"Fixed in db4a7c83adda270fd8ed19f6b3874ad92337b35c. Slide tracking now resets when the current market symbol changes, so market-to-market navigation can emit slide analytics again.","path":"app/components/UI/Perps/components/PerpsRelatedMarkets/PerpsRelatedMarkets.tsx","line":58,"outdated":false,"createdAt":"2026-05-28T10:12:11Z"}]}},{"id":"PRRT_kwDOCG4DHc6FW4fz","isResolved":true,"comments":{"nodes":[{"databaseId":3316873727,"author":{"login":"aganglada"},"body":"is this included on the racking repo","path":"app/components/UI/Perps/components/PerpsRelatedMarkets/PerpsRelatedMarkets.tsx","line":71,"outdated":false,"createdAt":"2026-05-28T09:49:20Z"},{"databaseId":3317017231,"author":{"login":"abretonc7s"},"body":"Out of scope for this PR — tracking-repo registration lives outside metamask-mobile; this PR keeps the mobile event usage and docs in this repo.","path":"app/components/UI/Perps/components/PerpsRelatedMarkets/PerpsRelatedMarkets.tsx","line":71,"outdated":false,"createdAt":"2026-05-28T10:12:13Z"}]}},{"id":"PRRT_kwDOCG4DHc6FW4wU","isResolved":true,"comments":{"nodes":[{"databaseId":3316875399,"author":{"login":"aganglada"},"body":"same here","path":"app/components/UI/Perps/