sor-dark.png\"></picture></a>&nbsp;<a href=\"https://cursor.com/agents?\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\"><picture><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-dark.png\"><source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: light)\" srcset=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-light.png\"><img alt=\"Fix in Web\" width=\"99\" height=\"28\" src=\"https://cursor.com/assets/images/fix-in-web-dark.png\"></picture></a></div>\n\n\n<sup>Reviewed by [Cursor Bugbot](https://cursor.com/bugbot) for commit db4a7c83adda270fd8ed19f6b3874ad92337b35c. Configure [here](https://www.cursor.com/dashboard/bugbot).</sup>\n","path":"app/components/UI/Perps/components/PerpsRelatedMarkets/PerpsRelatedMarkets.tsx","line":101,"outdated":false,"createdAt":"2026-05-28T10:17:35Z"}]}}]}}}}}